# 按照IT行业几个主流方向分类
def jtype(x):
    if operator.contains(x,'分析'):
        return '数据分析师'
    elif operator.contains(x,'开发'):
        return '开发工程师'
    elif operator.contains(x,'运维'):
        return '运维工程师'
    elif operator.contains(x,'前端'):
        return '前端工程师'
    elif operator.contains(x,'后端'):
        return '后端工程师'
    elif operator.contains(x,'大数据'):
        return '大数据工程师'
    elif operator.contains(x,'爬虫'):
        return '爬虫工程师'
    elif operator.contains(x,'人工智能'):
        return '人工智能工程师'
    elif operator.contains(x,'测试'):
        return '测试工程师'
    elif operator.contains(x,'标注'):
        return '数据标注师'
    elif operator.contains(x,'算法'):
        return '算法工程师'
    elif operator.contains(x,'实习'):
        return '实习生'
    else:
        return '其他'

def edu(x):
    if operator.contains(x,'不限'):
        return '学历不限'
    elif operator.contains(x,'博士'):
        return '博士'
    elif operator.contains(x,'硕士'):
        return '硕士'
    elif operator.contains(x,'本科'):
        return '本科'
    elif operator.contains(x,'大专'):
        return '大专'
    elif operator.contains(x,'高中'):
        return '高中'
    elif operator.contains(x,'中专'):
        return '中专'
    elif operator.contains(x,'初中'):
        return '初中'
    else:
        return '其他'
